description: The fund is an actively managed exchange-traded fund (“ETF”) that seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing up to 80% of its net assets (plus borrowings for investment purposes) in portfolio holdings expected to benefit, either directly or indirectly, from rising prices (i.e., inflation). The fund adviser seeks to identify securities of companies positioned to benefit from inflationary pressures. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Amplify Inflation Fighter ETF
